div.div: The general Manager contains specific managers, such as for connectors or pipelines. It acts as a proxy, bridging World <-> Managers with asynchronous channels.
Both the general Manager and the specific ones run in a separate task (following the actor model, as many more parts of Tremor).

div.div: This is how the connectors are first initialized. This may happen at runtime later on with `register_connector_type()` once the PDK is finished.
Note that unregistering PDK artifacts will not be implemented for now.
